    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Gacha Party》是一款塔防类游戏~</h2><br>某年某月，一种电子病毒在机器人中传播开来，原本用于家政服务的微型机器人发生了觉醒！它们不再为人类服务，反而将搞破坏奉为终极目标~<br><br>有人说：“要用魔法打败魔法”<br>于是——新一代的仿真机器人诞生！和微型机在各地决斗吧！<br><br>在《Gacha Party》中你可以体验到：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★可爱的角色形象设计，因地制宜的战斗特色(⊙ꇴ⊙)</h2>小小的人儿 + 大大的道具，看角色如何化用日常用品武装自己！<br>每个角色都有独一无二的战斗武器——饼干、键盘，亦或是一张老旧的CD！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231880/extras/8debd5d414592fd8fb0c0b07a67e4ec5.poster.avif?t=1684313878\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231880/extras/8debd5d414592fd8fb0c0b07a67e4ec5.webm?t=1684313878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231880/extras/8debd5d414592fd8fb0c0b07a67e4ec5.mp4?t=1684313878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★超级休闲塔防玩法ᕕ(ᐛ)ᕗ</h2>体验经典的塔防玩法，感受最原始的游戏热爱。<br>不同难度的关卡自由切换，看看谁能坚守最后的阵地~<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★各色风格主题场景(ꈍ﹃ ꈍ)</h2>二次元御宅小屋、国风茶台，各色房间主题场景自由体验！<br>在蛋糕、梦境、音乐、冰箱，甚至烤炉上抵御入侵，守护家园！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231880/extras/9b75316bbc3d2b12185f2908244ece87.poster.avif?t=1684313878\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231880/extras/9b75316bbc3d2b12185f2908244ece87.webm?t=1684313878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231880/extras/9b75316bbc3d2b12185f2908244ece87.mp4?t=1684313878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★创意工坊内置！人人都是创造者(≥▽≤)</h2>游戏内置创意工坊，所有玩法模式均可自由编辑、上传、分享！<br>让大伙看看谁才是创造之王~",
